                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mr-4 mt-0">
                <a href="https://tuist.io/docs/usage/getting-started/" target="_blank" class="inline-block text-sm p-4 rounded font-medium tracking-wide bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-700 text-white hover:from-primary hover:to-primary">Get started</a>
