                            TODO: switch to <%= CommandEvent.where("name = 'cache' AND subcommand = 'warm' AND created_at >= ?", 1.day.ago.to_datetime).count %>
                            once https://github.com/tuist/tuist/pull/2508 is released
                        !-->
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-white text-center bg-green-800 bg-opacity-50 hover:bg-opacity-75 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-xl font-semibold p-2"><%= t("home.stats.today_cache") %></div>
                </div>
            </div>
